org.mitre.provenance.plusobject

Class ProvenanceCollection

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mitre.provenance.plusobject.ProvenanceCollection
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AMPPDemo, AnalysisWorkflow, ContainmentDemo, DAGComponent, EvilCycle, HGDemo, IAWorkflow, ImpliedShaper, Motif, SimpleWorkflow, STraceLogger, SyntheticGraph, ViewedCollection

    public class ProvenanceCollection
extends Object
implements Cloneable
    A collection of provenance objects, nodes and edges. Basic provenance collections cannot be assumed to be well-connected. They do not necessarily comprise a graph. See LineageDAG for an example of an actual graph, which extends this class.
    Author:
    DMALLEN
    See Also:
    LineageDAG

      • addEdge

        public boolean addEdge(PLUSEdge edge,
                       boolean force)
        Add an edge to the collection.
        Parameters:
        edge - the edge to add.
        force - if true, this will be added overwriting anything similar already there. If false, the edge will be added only if its candidate nodes aren't already connected.
        Returns:
        true if the edge was added, false otherwise.

      • addActor

        public boolean addActor(PLUSActor a,
                        boolean force)
        Add a particular actor to the graph
        Parameters:
        a - the actor to add
        force - if true, add this actor even if it is already present, overwriting what was previously there. If false, ignore the actor if it is already present.
        Returns:
        true if it was added, false otherwise.

      • addNode

        public boolean addNode(PLUSObject obj,
                       boolean force)
        Add a particular node to the graph
        Parameters:

        force - if true, add this node to the graph even if it is already present, overwriting what was previously there. If false, ignore the node if it is already present.
        Returns:
        true if it was added, false otherwise.

      • removeNode

        public PLUSObject removeNode(PLUSObject node,
                             boolean removeIncidentEdges)
        Remove a node from the provenance collection.
        Parameters:
        node - the node to remove
        removeIncidentEdges - if true, incident edges to that node will also be removed. If false, they will remain.
        Returns:
        the node removed (if it was in the collection) or null if it did not exist in the collection.

      • removeNode
